data.description: DRAMATIC PRICE IMPROVEMENT! MOTIVATED SELLER. Welcome to the prestigious community of Silver Lake Estates in Grapevine, TX! Inside, this spacious home offers three distinct living areas, providing space for relaxation, socializing, and family gatherings. Whether you're hosting formal events, unwinding in the cozy bonus room, or enjoying game night in the generously sized game room with wet bar, there's space for every occasion. The heart of this home is the backyard oasis complete with outdoor kitchen, perfect for hosting barbecues and al fresco dining experiences. Entertain family and friends with the sparkling pool, spa, and fire feature. You'll appreciate the dedicated office that offers privacy and productivity for remote professionals. This home is waiting for your personal touch. The Silver Lake community is renowned for its family-friendly atmosphere and top-rated schools. With easy access to major highways and the vibrant culture of Grapevine, you'll have everything you need.
